Version 1.1
DMA from the on-chip memory using a line buffer. This lets you see the
decoding happen in real time. Also update the version of Libpng to 1.6.37.
The goal of this version is to support the fx-CG50.

Version 1.003
Uses full frame and update Libpng to version 1.6.21.

Version 1.002
Another minor release this fixes a minor scaling bug and uses an up to date
version of Libpng (version 1.6.16).

Version 1.001
Minor bugfix: fixed harmless warning from Libpng

Version 1
Initial release
